### Parameters

The model is relatively economical:
- $m_\chi$ — mass of composite particles
- $\lambda_p$ — self-interaction / potential strength
- $g, h, \epsilon$ — coupling constants (baryon, flow, magnetic)
- $\Gamma$ — relaxation rate for adaptive dynamics

